== This is not tried, just guidelines. ==

=== C.H.I.P ===
	R8 - 1GHz
	512MB RAM
	4GB high-speed storage
	WiFi B/G/N
	Bluetooth 4.0
	I/O 3v3	

=== Likely require change to ===
=== uboot-env.bin ===
add uInitrd, and distributions on mtd, usb storage etc.
=== rootfs.tgz ===
binaries- busybox etc.
=== rootfs/init ===
Probably read some .rc file from pendrive to get distro menu.  ( No more flash required to NAND.) Add a distribution subdir, and modify the .rc file
=== Rootfs is just a copy from Odroid U3. ===
		

